<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/welcome_style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    We are committed to providing the best service possible and ensuring customer satisfaction. Our mission is to 
                    deliver top-notch products and services that exceed expectations and make a positive impact on our community.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Team</h2>
                <p>
                    Our team is made up of dedicated professionals with a passion for what they do. We work together to achieve 
                    our goals and continuously strive for excellence. Meet our talented team members who are always ready to help you.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions or need more information, feel free to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. We would 
                    love to hear from you and assist you with any inquiries you may have.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
